# Desktop Critical Rule
# Purpose: Prevent screenshot clutter with low-risk automation
# Status: ACTIVE (Phase 1 - Critical Only)

## Rule: Auto-organize screenshots (1-hour buffer)
## Prevents accidental processing of screenshots you just took
Conditions:
- Name contains "Screenshot"
- Kind is Image
- Date Added is not in the last 1 hour

Actions:
- Import to Photos.app
- Move to Trash

---

# Implementation Notes:
# - Import this rule into Hazel app manually: Hazel → Desktop → Import Rules
# - 1-hour buffer prevents processing screenshots you just took
# - Low risk: Screenshots are backed up to iCloud Photos before deletion
# - High value: Keeps Desktop clean without manual effort

